  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Most screen readers do <strong>not</strong> announce strikethrough &mdash; the visual is lost</li>
      <li>Add <code>visually-hidden</code> context for critical information like pricing</li>
      <li>Ensure surrounding text provides context for why content is struck through</li>
    </ul>

